Defeated by the Envoy
[trigger none]
[vignette dungeons/the_city]

"Easy now, you took a hard hit."

Torben leans over you. He looks like hell. You're back in the plaza somehow, the strange light filtering in through the dome. 

The right side of the cartograph's face is a giant bruise. "I've had worse," he assures you.

He gestures toward a heap of armor, the remains of the thing that felled you, "Though you might like to keep it. Souvenir of sorts. Might fetch a good price in town, if you haul it back."

"What... was that thing?" you ask.

"A mailman, if you can believe it. Have a look at this."

Torben hands you a letter.

choices:
  * Take the letter 
  +advance_time 4 no_meal
